  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK174">
<l>ilameṉṟu veḵkutal ceyyār pulamveṉṟa</l>
<l>puṉmaiyil kāṭci yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise who have conquered their senses and are free from crime, will not covet (the things of others), with the thought "we are destitute."</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
